Different operating system used for cybersecurity are as follows:
1.parrot os
2.kali linux
3.ubuntu
4.blackarch
5.node zero
6.caine
7.puppy linux
8.linux kodachi

Steps to download kali linux OS

Download iso file from kali linux page
In vmware workstation create new vm
Then give the path where iso file is downloaded 
Then give next
It asks for vm name and select the max disk size
Click finish

Open Vm workstation to install kali OS
click on play vm
click graphical install
select passward hostname language country
installation is done kali linux is ready to use


